x | Delete, Cut Character
xp | Swap Two Adjacent Letters

r | Replace a Single Character
R | Replace Characters Until ESC
J | Join Line Below to Current Line, Space Between
gJ | Join Line Below to Current Line, No Space
gwip | Reflow Paragraph
